apps.description:
We forked FDroid in order to give the iodé repository a higher priority
than prebuilt repos, and to reset the repos database if needed (particularly,
for already running instances of the iodéOS ROM).
apps.name: F-Droid
FakeStore
apps.summary: Redistribution of official versions of FakeStore for iodeOS

apps.description:
This Firefox fork has the following features:

* Telemetry disabled and its corresponding code partially removed (trackers Adjust, BreadCrumb, Google AdMob, LeanPlum).
* Alternative search engine: Qwant is is the default search engine.
* Several search engines added: Brave, Ecosia, Gibiru, Metager, Mojeek, Qwant light, Startpage, several Searx instances, Swisscows, You.com.
* Qwant replaces Google in the hard-coded top sites.
* Several menu entries removed: Telemetry, USB debugging, Vote on Google Play.
apps.name: Iodé Browser
apps.summary: Browser based on Mozilla Firefox, with alternative default search engine and no telemetry

apps.authorName: iodé Team (forked from official LineageOS Jelly)
apps.description: Jelly is the official browser of LineageOS. We tweaked it to set Qwant as the default search engine and suggestions provider, and added several alternative search engines (Brave, DuckDuckGo, Ecosia, Gibiru, Metager, Mojeek, several Searx instances, Startpage, Swisscows, You.com).
apps.name: Jelly
apps.summary: iodéOS version of LineageOS browser, with alternative search engines
